touch -am 1231235999 $$.touch >/dev/null 2>&1
if test ! -f 1231235999 && test -f $$.touch; then
  shar_touch=touch
else
  shar_touch=:
  echo 'WARNING: not restoring timestamps'
fi
rm -f 1231235999 $$.touch
#
# ============= Lasso2/Doc/Doc/opt.knot.ps ==============
if test ! -d 'Lasso2'; then
  echo 'x - creating directory Lasso2'
  mkdir 'Lasso2'
fi
if test ! -d 'Lasso2/Doc'; then
  echo 'x - creating directory Lasso2/Doc'
  mkdir 'Lasso2/Doc'
fi
if test ! -d 'Lasso2/Doc/Doc'; then
  echo 'x - creating directory Lasso2/Doc/Doc'
  mkdir 'Lasso2/Doc/Doc'
fi
if test -f 'Lasso2/Doc/Doc/opt.knot.ps' && test X"$1" != X"-c"; then
  echo 'x - skipping Lasso2/Doc/Doc/opt.knot.ps (File already exists)'
else
  echo 'x - extracting Lasso2/Doc/Doc/opt.knot.ps (text)'
  sed 's/^X//' << 'SHAR_EOF' > 'Lasso2/Doc/Doc/opt.knot.ps' &&
%!PS-Adobe-2.0
%%Creator: dvips(k) 5.78 Copyright 1998 Radical Eye Software (www.radicaleye.com)
%%Title: main.dvi
%%Pages: 6
%%PageOrder: Ascend
%%BoundingBox: 0 0 596 842
%%DocumentFonts: CMBX12 CMR12 CMBX10 CMR10 CMTI10 CMMI7 CMSY7 MSBM7
%%+ CMMI5 CMMI10 CMSY10 CMR7 CMR8 CMEX10 CMBX7 CMR5 Helvetica
%%EndComments
%DVIPSCommandLine: dvips main -o opt.knot.ps
%DVIPSParameters: dpi=400, compressed, comments removed
%DVIPSSource:  TeX output 1998.11.03:1207
%%BeginProcSet: texc.pro
/TeXDict 300 dict def TeXDict begin /N{def}def /B{bind def}N /S{exch}N
/X{S N}B /TR{translate}N /isls false N /vsize 11 72 mul N /hsize 8.5 72
mul N /landplus90{false}def /@rigin{isls{[0 landplus90{1 -1}{-1 1}
ifelse 0 0 0]concat}if 72 Resolution div 72 VResolution div neg scale
isls{landplus90{VResolution 72 div vsize mul 0 exch}{Resolution -72 div
hsize mul 0}ifelse TR}if Resolution VResolution vsize -72 div 1 add mul
TR[matrix currentmatrix{dup dup round sub abs 0.00001 lt{round}if}
forall round exch round exch]setmatrix}N /@landscape{/isls true N}B
/@manualfeed{statusdict /manualfeed true put}B /@copies{/#copies X}B
/FMat[1 0 0 -1 0 0]N /FBB[0 0 0 0]N /nn 0 N /IE 0 N /ctr 0 N /df-tail{
/nn 8 dict N nn begin /FontType 3 N /FontMatrix fntrx N /FontBBox FBB N
string /base X array /BitMaps X /BuildChar{CharBuilder}N /Encoding IE N
end dup{/foo setfont}2 array copy cvx N load 0 nn put /ctr 0 N[}B /df{
/sf 1 N /fntrx FMat N df-tail}B /dfs{div /sf X /fntrx[sf 0 0 sf neg 0 0]
N df-tail}B /E{pop nn dup definefont setfont}B /ch-width{ch-data dup
length 5 sub get}B /ch-height{ch-data dup length 4 sub get}B /ch-xoff{
128 ch-data dup length 3 sub get sub}B /ch-yoff{ch-data dup length 2 sub
get 127 sub}B /ch-dx{ch-data dup length 1 sub get}B /ch-image{ch-data
dup type /stringtype ne{ctr get /ctr ctr 1 add N}if}B /id 0 N /rw 0 N
/rc 0 N /gp 0 N /cp 0 N /G 0 N /sf 0 N /CharBuilder{save 3 1 roll S dup
/base get 2 index get S /BitMaps get S get /ch-data X pop /ctr 0 N ch-dx
0 ch-xoff ch-yoff ch-height sub ch-xoff ch-width add ch-yoff
setcachedevice ch-width ch-height true[1 0 0 -1 -.1 ch-xoff sub ch-yoff
X.1 sub]/id ch-image N /rw ch-width 7 add 8 idiv string N /rc 0 N /gp 0 N
/cp 0 N{rc 0 ne{rc 1 sub /rc X rw}{G}ifelse}imagemask restore}B /G{{id
gp get /gp gp 1 add N dup 18 mod S 18 idiv pl S get exec}loop}B /adv{cp
add /cp X}B /chg{rw cp id gp 4 index getinterval putinterval dup gp add
/gp X adv}B /nd{/cp 0 N rw exit}B /lsh{rw cp 2 copy get dup 0 eq{pop 1}{
dup 255 eq{pop 254}{dup dup add 255 and S 1 and or}ifelse}ifelse put 1
adv}B /rsh{rw cp 2 copy get dup 0 eq{pop 128}{dup 255 eq{pop 127}{dup 2
idiv S 128 and or}ifelse}ifelse put 1 adv}B /clr{rw cp 2 index string
putinterval adv}B /set{rw cp fillstr 0 4 index getinterval putinterval
adv}B /fillstr 18 string 0 1 17{2 copy 255 put pop}for N /pl[{adv 1 chg}
{adv 1 chg nd}{1 add chg}{1 add chg nd}{adv lsh}{adv lsh nd}{adv rsh}{
adv rsh nd}{1 add adv}{/rc X nd}{1 add set}{1 add clr}{adv 2 chg}{adv 2
chg nd}{pop nd}]dup{bind pop}forall N /D{/cc X dup type /stringtype ne{]
}if nn /base get cc ctr put nn /BitMaps get S ctr S sf 1 ne{dup dup
length 1 sub dup 2 index S get sf div put}if put /ctr ctr 1 add N}B /I{
cc 1 add D}B /bop{userdict /bop-hook known{bop-hook}if /SI save N @rigin
0 0 moveto /V matrix currentmatrix dup 1 get dup mul exch 0 get dup mul
add .99 lt{/QV}{/RV}ifelse load def pop pop}N /eop{SI restore userdict
/eop-hook known{eop-hook}if showpage}N /@start{userdict /start-hook
known{start-hook}if pop /VResolution X /Resolution X 1000 div /DVImag X
/IE 256 array N 2 string 0 1 255{IE S dup 360 add 36 4 index cvrs cvn
put}for pop 65781.76 div /vsize X 65781.76 div /hsize X}N /p{show}N
/RMat[1 0 0 -1 0 0]N /BDot 260 string N /rulex 0 N /ruley 0 N /v{/ruley
XX /rulex X V}B /V{}B /RV statusdict begin /product where{pop false[
(Display)(NeXT)(LaserWriter 16/600)]{dup length product length le{dup
length product exch 0 exch getinterval eq{pop true exit}if}{pop}ifelse}
forall}{false}ifelse end{{gsave TR -.1 .1 TR 1 1 scale rulex ruley false
RMat{BDot}imagemask grestore}}{{gsave TR -.1 .1 TR rulex ruley scale 1 1
false RMat{BDot}imagemask grestore}}ifelse B /QV{gsave newpath transform
round exch round exch itransform moveto rulex 0 rlineto 0 ruley neg
rlineto rulex neg 0 rlineto fill grestore}B /a{moveto}B /delta 0 N /tail
{dup /delta X 0 rmoveto}B /M{S p delta add tail}B /b{S p tail}B /c{-4 M}
B /d{-3 M}B /e{-2 M}B /f{-1 M}B /g{0 M}B /h{1 M}B /i{2 M}B /j{3 M}B /k{
4 M}B /w{0 rmoveto}B /l{p -4 w}B /m{p -3 w}B /n{p -2 w}B /o{p -1 w}B /q{
p 1 w}B /r{p 2 w}B /s{p 3 w}B /t{p 4 w}B /x{0 S rmoveto}B /y{3 2 roll p
a}B /bos{/SS save N}B /eos{SS restore}B end
X
%%EndProcSet
%%BeginProcSet: 8r.enc
% @@psencodingfile@{
%   author = "S. Rahtz, P. MacKay, Alan Jeffrey, B. Horn, K. Berry",
%   version = "0.6",
%   date = "22 June 1996",
%   filename = "8r.enc",
%   email = "kb@@mail.tug.org",
%   address = "135 Center Hill Rd. // Plymouth, MA 02360",
%   codetable = "ISO/ASCII",
%   checksum = "119     662    4424",
%   docstring = "Encoding for TrueType or Type 1 fonts to be used with TeX."
% @}
% 
% Idea is to have all the characters normally included in Type 1 fonts
% available for typesetting. This is effectively the characters in Adobe
% Standard Encoding + ISO Latin 1 + extra characters from Lucida.
% 
% Character code assignments were made as follows:
% 
% (1) the Windows ANSI characters are almost all in their Windows ANSI
% positions, because some Windows users cannot easily reencode the
% fonts, and it makes no difference on other systems. The only Windows
% ANSI characters not available are those that make no sense for
% typesetting -- rubout (127 decimal), nobreakspace (160), softhyphen
% (173). quotesingle and grave are moved just because it's such an
% irritation not having them in TeX positions.
% 
% (2) Remaining characters are assigned arbitrarily to the lower part
% of the range, avoiding 0, 10 and 13 in case we meet dumb software.
% 
% (3) Y&Y Lucida Bright includes some extra text characters; in the
% hopes that other PostScript fonts, perhaps created for public
% consumption, will include them, they are included starting at 0x12.
% 
% (4) Remaining positions left undefined are for use in (hopefully)
% upward-compatible revisions, if someday more characters are generally
% available.
% 
% (5) hyphen appears twice for compatibility with both ASCII and Windows.
% 
/TeXBase1Encoding [
% 0x00 (encoded characters from Adobe Standard not in Windows 3.1)
X  /.notdef /dotaccent /fi /fl
X  /fraction /hungarumlaut /Lslash /lslash
X  /ogonek /ring /.notdef
X  /breve /minus /.notdef 
% These are the only two remaining unencoded characters, so may as
% well include them.
X  /Zcaron /zcaron 
% 0x10
X /caron /dotlessi 
% (unusual TeX characters available in, e.g., Lucida Bright)
X /dotlessj /ff /ffi /ffl 
X /.notdef /.notdef /.notdef /.notdef
X /.notdef /.notdef /.notdef /.notdef
X % very contentious; it's so painful not having quoteleft and quoteright
X % at 96 and 145 that we move the things normally found there down to here.
X /grave /quotesingle 
% 0x20 (ASCII begins)
X /space /exclam /quotedbl /numbersign
X /dollar /percent /ampersand /quoteright
X /parenleft /parenright /asterisk /plus /comma /hyphen /period /slash
% 0x30
X /zero /one /two /three /four /five /six /seven
X /eight /nine /colon /semicolon /less /equal /greater /question
% 0x40
X /at /A /B /C /D /E /F /G /H /I /J /K /L /M /N /O
% 0x50
X /P /Q /R /S /T /U /V /W
X /X /Y /Z /bracketleft /backslash /bracketright /asciicircum /underscore
% 0x60
X /quoteleft /a /b /c /d /e /f /g /h /i /j /k /l /m /n /o
% 0x70
X /p /q /r /s /t /u /v /w
X /x /y /z /braceleft /bar /braceright /asciitilde
X /.notdef % rubout; ASCII ends
% 0x80
X /.notdef /.notdef /quotesinglbase /florin
X /quotedblbase /ellipsis /dagger /daggerdbl
X /circumflex /perthousand /Scaron /guilsinglleft
X /OE /.notdef /.notdef /.notdef
% 0x90
X /.notdef /.notdef /.notdef /quotedblleft
X /quotedblright /bullet /endash /emdash
X /tilde /trademark /scaron /guilsinglright
X /oe /.notdef /.notdef /Ydieresis
% 0xA0
X /.notdef % nobreakspace
X /exclamdown /cent /sterling
X /currency /yen /brokenbar /section
X /dieresis /copyright /ordfeminine /guillemotleft
X /logicalnot
X /hyphen % Y&Y (also at 45); Windows' softhyphen
X /registered
X /macron
% 0xD0
X /degree /plusminus /twosuperior /threesuperior
X /acute /mu /paragraph /periodcentered
X /cedilla /onesuperior /ordmasculine /guillemotright
X /onequarter /onehalf /threequarters /questiondown
% 0xC0
X /Agrave /Aacute /Acircumflex /Atilde /Adieresis /Aring /AE /Ccedilla
X /Egrave /Eacute /Ecircumflex /Edieresis
X /Igrave /Iacute /Icircumflex /Idieresis
% 0xD0
X /Eth /Ntilde /Ograve /Oacute
X /Ocircumflex /Otilde /Odieresis /multiply
X /Oslash /Ugrave /Uacute /Ucircumflex
X /Udieresis /Yacute /Thorn /germandbls
% 0xE0
X /agrave /aacute /acircumflex /atilde
X /adieresis /aring /ae /ccedilla
X /egrave /eacute /ecircumflex /edieresis
X /igrave /iacute /icircumflex /idieresis
% 0xF0
X /eth /ntilde /ograve /oacute
X /ocircumflex /otilde /odieresis /divide
X /oslash /ugrave /uacute /ucircumflex
X /udieresis /yacute /thorn /ydieresis
] def
X
%%EndProcSet
%%BeginProcSet: texps.pro
TeXDict begin /rf{findfont dup length 1 add dict begin{1 index /FID ne 2
index /UniqueID ne and{def}{pop pop}ifelse}forall[1 index 0 6 -1 roll
exec 0 exch 5 -1 roll VResolution Resolution div mul neg 0 0]/Metrics
exch def dict begin Encoding{exch dup type /integertype ne{pop pop 1 sub
dup 0 le{pop}{[}ifelse}{FontMatrix 0 get div Metrics 0 get div def}
ifelse}forall Metrics /Metrics currentdict end def[2 index currentdict
end definefont 3 -1 roll makefont /setfont cvx]cvx def}def /ObliqueSlant
{dup sin S cos div neg}B /SlantFont{4 index mul add}def /ExtendFont{3 -1
roll mul exch}def /ReEncodeFont{/Encoding exch def}def end
X
%%EndProcSet
%%BeginProcSet: special.pro
TeXDict begin /SDict 200 dict N SDict begin /@SpecialDefaults{/hs 612 N
/vs 792 N /ho 0 N /vo 0 N /hsc 1 N /vsc 1 N /ang 0 N /CLIP 0 N /rwiSeen
false N /rhiSeen false N /letter{}N /note{}N /a4{}N /legal{}N}B
/@scaleunit 100 N /@hscale{@scaleunit div /hsc X}B /@vscale{@scaleunit
div /vsc X}B /@hsize{/hs X /CLIP 1 N}B /@vsize{/vs X /CLIP 1 N}B /@clip{
/CLIP 2 N}B /@hoffset{/ho X}B /@voffset{/vo X}B /@angle{/ang X}B /@rwi{
10 div /rwi X /rwiSeen true N}B /@rhi{10 div /rhi X /rhiSeen true N}B
/@llx{/llx X}B /@lly{/lly X}B /@urx{/urx X}B /@ury{/ury X}B /magscale
true def end /@MacSetUp{userdict /md known{userdict /md get type
/dicttype eq{userdict begin md length 10 add md maxlength ge{/md md dup
length 20 add dict copy def}if end md begin /letter{}N /note{}N /legal{}
N /od{txpose 1 0 mtx defaultmatrix dtransform S atan/pa X newpath
clippath mark{transform{itransform moveto}}{transform{itransform lineto}
}{6 -2 roll transform 6 -2 roll transform 6 -2 roll transform{
itransform 6 2 roll itransform 6 2 roll itransform 6 2 roll curveto}}{{
closepath}}pathforall newpath counttomark array astore /gc xdf pop ct 39
0 put 10 fz 0 fs 2 F/|______Courier fnt invertflag{PaintBlack}if}N
/txpose{pxs pys scale ppr aload pop por{noflips{pop S neg S TR pop 1 -1
scale}if xflip yflip and{pop S neg S TR 180 rotate 1 -1 scale ppr 3 get
ppr 1 get neg sub neg ppr 2 get ppr 0 get neg sub neg TR}if xflip yflip
not and{pop S neg S TR pop 180 rotate ppr 3 get ppr 1 get neg sub neg 0
TR}if yflip xflip not and{ppr 1 get neg ppr 0 get neg TR}if}{noflips{TR
pop pop 270 rotate 1 -1 scale}if xflip yflip and{TR pop pop 90 rotate 1
-1 scale ppr 3 get ppr 1 get neg sub neg ppr 2 get ppr 0 get neg sub neg
TR}if xflip yflip not and{TR pop pop 90 rotate ppr 3 get ppr 1 get neg
sub neg 0 TR}if yflip xflip not and{TR pop pop 270 rotate ppr 2 get ppr
0 get neg sub neg 0 S TR}if}ifelse scaleby96{ppr aload pop 4 -1 roll add
2 div 3 1 roll add 2 div 2 copy TR .96 dup scale neg S neg S TR}if}N /cp
{pop pop showpage pm restore}N end}if}if}N /normalscale{Resolution 72
div VResolution 72 div neg scale magscale{DVImag dup scale}if 0 setgray}
N /psfts{S 65781.76 div N}N /startTexFig{/psf$SavedState save N userdict
maxlength dict begin /magscale true def normalscale currentpoint TR
/psf$ury psfts /psf$urx psfts /psf$lly psfts /psf$llx psfts /psf$y psfts
/psf$x psfts currentpoint /psf$cy X /psf$cx X /psf$sx psf$x psf$urx
psf$llx sub div N /psf$sy psf$y psf$ury psf$lly sub div N psf$sx psf$sy
scale psf$cx psf$sx div psf$llx sub psf$cy psf$sy div psf$ury sub TR
/showpage{}N /erasepage{}N /copypage{}N /p 3 def @MacSetUp}N /doclip{
psf$llx psf$lly psf$urx psf$ury currentpoint 6 2 roll newpath 4 copy 4 2
roll moveto 6 -1 roll S lineto S lineto S lineto closepath clip newpath
moveto}N /endTexFig{end psf$SavedState restore}N /@beginspecial{SDict
begin /SpecialSave save N gsave normalscale currentpoint TR
@SpecialDefaults count /ocount X /dcount countdictstack N}N /@setspecial
{CLIP 1 eq{newpath 0 0 moveto hs 0 rlineto 0 vs rlineto hs neg 0 rlineto
closepath clip}if ho vo TR hsc vsc scale ang rotate rwiSeen{rwi urx llx
sub div rhiSeen{rhi ury lly sub div}{dup}ifelse scale llx neg lly neg TR
}{rhiSeen{rhi ury lly sub div dup scale llx neg lly neg TR}if}ifelse
CLIP 2 eq{newpath llx lly moveto urx lly lineto urx ury lineto llx ury
lineto closepath clip}if /showpage{}N /erasepage{}N /copypage{}N newpath
}N /@endspecial{count ocount sub{pop}repeat countdictstack dcount sub{
end}repeat grestore SpecialSave restore end}N /@defspecial{SDict begin}
N /@fedspecial{end}B /li{lineto}B /rl{rlineto}B /rc{rcurveto}B /np{
/SaveX currentpoint /SaveY X N 1 setlinecap newpath}N /st{stroke SaveX
SaveY moveto}N /fil{fill SaveX SaveY moveto}N /ellipse{/endangle X
/startangle X /yrad X /xrad X /savematrix matrix currentmatrix N TR xrad
yrad scale 0 0 1 startangle endangle arc savematrix setmatrix}N end
X
%%EndProcSet

/version (1.00B) readonly def

/FullName (CMR5) readonly def
/FamilyName (Computer Modern) readonly def
/Weight (Medium) readonly def
/ItalicAngle 0 def
/isFixedPitch false def
end readonly def
/FontName /CMR5 def
/PaintType 0 def
/FontType 1 def
/FontMatrix [0.001 0 0 0.001 0 0] readonly def
/Encoding 256 array
0 1 255 {1 index exch /.notdef put} for
dup 49 /one put
dup 50 /two put
readonly def

/UniqueID 5000788 def

%%Page: 3 3
3 2 bop 40 -2 a
X currentpoint currentpoint translate 0.29169 0.29169 scale neg exch
neg exch translate
X 40 -2 a 40 -2 a
X gsave currentpoint currentpoint translate 270 neg rotate neg exch
neg exch translate
X 40 -2 a @beginspecial
20 @llx 35 @lly 592 @urx 757 @ury 5720 @rwi @setspecial
%%BeginDocument: Figures/fullmin.100.ps
150 dict begin gsave
/bd{bind def}def
/PVer 3200 def
% drawing commands
/I{Coord SetPage 1 setlinecap 1 setlinejoin
X    LineTypes{RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}forall
X    /Helvetica findfont
X    PointSize RastersPerPoint mul Cex mul scalefont setfont
X    /Colors GColors def
}bd
/BWOp{
X    bw{currentrgbcolor add add 2.9 gt{1}{0}ifelse setgray}if
X    exec
X    bw{CurSc Sc}if
}bd
/IBu{}def
/B{newpath}bd
/E{{stroke}BWOp}bd
/C{currentpoint Penup{newpath}{E}ifelse moveto}bd
/F{closepath eofill}bd
/M{moveto}bd
/L{lineto}bd
/Pu{load /XEQ exch def /Penup true def}bd
/Pd{/XEQ{}def /Penup false def}bd
/Px{currentdict /XEQ known{XEQ}if}bd
/h{Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/j{neg Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/k{exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/l{neg exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/m{moveto Penup{Px}if}bd
/x{0 Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/y{0 exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/w{neg x}bd
/z{neg y}bd
/a{B M dup y exch x neg y closepath}bd
/b{a eofill}bd
/c{a E}bd
/A{PageBegin BackCol 0 ge
X    {CurSc gsave 0 SC Page aload pop
X    exch 4 -1 roll dup 5 1 roll sub 3 1 roll exch dup 4 1 roll sub 4 2 roll b
X    grestore SC}if
}bd
/Ph{gsave Pch-x Pch-y rmoveto Show grestore}bd
/Pc{Pch Ph}bd
/T{/Adjust exch def gsave translate StringRot rotate 0 0 moveto
X    dup stringwidth pop neg Adjust mul 0 rmoveto
X    currentpoint translate TextShow grestore}bd
/X{erasepage InPage{PageEnd}if}bd
/Z{gsave showpage grestore PageEnd}bd
/W{grestore end}bd
% parameter setting commands
/saveAt{Attr begin
X    /Atlinewidth currentlinewidth def
X    /Atfont currentfont def
X    /Atdash currentdash 2 array astore def
X    /AtSc CurSc def
end}bd
/restAt{Attr begin
X    Atlinewidth Atfont Atdash AtSc
X    end
X    SC aload pop setdash setfont setlinewidth
}bd
/SC{dup dup 0 eq
X    {pop BackIdx
X        {BackCol dup 0 lt {pop 1 setgray} {Sc}ifelse}
X        {/Colors BColor def 1 Sc}ifelse}
X    {/Colors GColors def Sc}ifelse
X    /CurSc exch def
}bd
/St{1 sub LineTypes dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get 0 setdash}bd
/Sw{abs 2 div RastersPerPoint mul setlinewidth SetClip}bd
/Sp{dup 42 eq{pop IBu}{Pch exch 0 exch put SetPchSize}ifelse}bd
/Sx{dup Cex div /Ratio exch def
X     /Cex exch def
X     currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
X     /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
X     /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
X     /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sg{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Figure astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sr{/StringRot exch def}bd
/Sh{/CharRot exch def}bd
/Sd{0 eq /ClipToPlot exch def SetClip}bd
/Iv{/InPage false def/Clip 4 array def/Page 4 array def
X    /Figure [0 0 1 1] def/Plot [0 0 1 1] def/ClipToPlot true def
X    /Cex 1 def/Outline false def
X    /Pch 1 string def/Pch-x 0 def/Pch-y 0 def/Text-y 0 def
X    /LineTypes [ % in default units
X        [] [1 2] [4 4] [8 4] [13 3] [16 2 2 2] [8 2 2 2] [1 13] [6 5] [12 4]
X    ] def
X    /Attr 5 dict def/CurSc 1 def/Penup false def/XEQ{}def
}bd
/Rem{2 copy div floor mul sub floor cvi}bd
/RastersPerPoint{RastersPerInch 72 div}bd
/ScaleArray{/Factor exch def /Array exch def
X    0 1 Array length 1 sub
X    {dup Array exch get Factor mul Array 3 1 roll put}for}bd
/Coord{Region aload pop /uy exch def /ux exch def /ly exch def /lx exch def
X    uy ly sub ux lx sub Landscape{exch}if /Width exch def /Height exch def
X    lx ly translate Landscape{90 rotate 0 Height neg translate}if
X    1 RastersPerPoint div dup scale}bd
/SetPchSize{gsave
X    newpath 0 0 moveto Pch false charpath flattenpath pathbbox
X    exch 3 1 roll
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-y exch def
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-x exch def
X    grestore}bd
/Show{Outline{false charpath E}{{show}BWOp}ifelse}bd
/SimpleShow{0 Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto Show}bd
/FancyShow{
X    /RotDiff exch def
X    /Cos RotDiff cos abs def
X    /Sin RotDiff sin abs def
X    {
X        ( ) dup 0 4 -1 roll put
X        dup stringwidth pop /CharWidth exch def
X        Cos 0 eq{
X            Text-y Sin div
X        }{
X            Sin 0 eq{
X                CharWidth Cos div
X            }{
X                Text-y Sin div dup
X                CharWidth Cos div dup
X                4 1 roll lt{exch pop}{pop}ifelse
X            }ifelse
X        }ifelse 2 div /CharDist exch def
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X        gsave
X            RotDiff rotate
X            CharWidth 2 div neg Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto
X            Show
X        grestore
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X    }forall
}bd
/TextShow{
X    CharRot StringRot sub dup 0 eq{pop SimpleShow}{FancyShow}ifelse
}bd
/BoxClip{/CLW currentlinewidth def
X    2{CLW add 4 1 roll}repeat
X    2{CLW sub 4 1 roll}repeat
X    % initclip
X    saveAt grestore gsave restAt
X    newpath 2 index exch 2 index exch dup 6 index exch
X    moveto 3{lineto}repeat closepath clip newpath}bd
/Subregion{
X    7 dict begin/A exch def/Uy exch def/Ux exch def/Ly exch def/Lx exch def
X    Ux Lx sub A 0 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 1 get mul Ly add
X    Ux Lx sub A 2 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 3 get mul Ly add end}bd
/SetFigure{Page aload pop Figure Subregion}bd
/SetPlot{SetFigure Plot Subregion}bd
/SetClip{ClipToPlot{SetPlot}{SetFigure}ifelse BoxClip}bd
/SetPage{0 0 Width Height Page astore RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}bd
/PageBegin{save /PageContext exch def /InPage true def gsave}bd
/PageEnd{grestore PageContext restore /InPage false def}bd
/SImage{
X    dup /Bits exch def 8 exch idiv /PerByte exch def
X    /Ht exch def /Wid exch def
X    1 Wid div 1 Ht div scale
X    /saveSc CurSc def /Colors IColors def
X    /curstr Wid PerByte add 1 sub PerByte idiv string def
X    /MaskByte 16#ff Bits 8 sub bitshift def
X    1 1 Ht{
X        currentfile curstr readhexstring pop pop
X        /CurPos 0 def
X        /Left PerByte def
X        1 1 Wid{
X            Left PerByte eq{
X                /CurByte curstr CurPos get def
X                /MaskMove -8 Bits add def
X                /CurPos CurPos 1 add def
X            }if
X            CurByte MaskMove bitshift MaskByte and
X            dup 0 gt{
X                Sc
X                exch dup 3 1 roll B M 1 z 1 w 1 y F
X            }{pop pop}ifelse
X            Left 1 sub dup /Left exch def 0 le
X            {/Left PerByte def}
X            {/MaskMove MaskMove Bits add def}ifelse
X        }for
X        pop
X    }for
X    /Colors GColors def saveSc Sc
}bd
/Ic {} bd
/Sc {
X    dup dup 1 lt exch 0 ge and
X    {1 exch sub setgray}  % explicit gray level [0,1)
X    {1 sub Colors dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     dup type /arraytype eq {aload pop setrgbcolor} {setgray} ifelse
X    } ifelse
} bd
/If {} bd
/Sf {dup 0 lt /Outline exch def abs
X     1 sub Fonts dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     findfont PointSize Cex mul RastersPerPoint mul scalefont dup setfont
X     dup /FontMatrix get /Matrix exch def /FontBBox get aload pop
X     Matrix transform 4 2 roll Matrix transform
X     exch pop add /Text-y exch def pop SetPchSize} bd
% fixed controlling parameters
/Landscape true def
/Region [20.88 35.0886 591.12 756.911] def
/bw statusdict begin /processcolors where
{pop processcolors} {1} ifelse end 1 eq
X def
/RastersPerInch 300 def
/PointSize 14 def
/Fonts [
X	/Helvetica
X	/Courier
X	/Times-Roman
X	/Helvetica-Oblique
X	/Helvetica-Bold
X	/Helvetica-BoldOblique
X	/Courier-Oblique
X	/Courier-Bold
X	/Courier-BoldOblique
X	/Times-Italic
X	/Times-Bold
X	/Times-BoldItalic
X	/Symbol
X	/AvantGarde-Book
X	/AvantGarde-BookOblique
X	/AvantGarde-Demi
X	/AvantGarde-DemiOblique
X	/Bookman-Demi
X	/Bookman-DemiItalic
X	/Bookman-Light
X	/Bookman-LightItalic
X	/Helvetica-Narrow
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Bold
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-BoldOblique
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Oblique
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Roman
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Bold
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Italic
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-BoldItalic
X	/Palatino-Roman
X	/Palatino-Bold
X	/Palatino-Italic
X	/Palatino-BoldItalic
X	/ZapfChancery-MediumItalic
X	/ZapfDingbats
] def
/GColors [
X	0
X	0.6
X	0.3
X	0.9
X	0.4
X	0.7
X	0.1
X	0.5
X	0.8
X	0.2
] def
/BackIdx true def
/BackCol -1 def
/IColors [
X	0.933333

] def
/Colors GColors def
/IBu {Pch 0 8#267 put SetPchSize} def
/Bu {Pc} def

X @endspecial 3218 -2 a
X currentpoint grestore moveto
X 3218 -2 a 40 -2 a
X currentpoint currentpoint translate 1 0.29169 div 1 0.29169 div scale
neg exch neg exch translate
X 40 -2 a 40 931
a
X currentpoint currentpoint translate 0.29169 0.29169 scale neg exch
neg exch translate
X 40 931 a 40 931 a
X gsave currentpoint currentpoint translate 270 neg rotate neg exch
neg exch translate
X 40 931 a @beginspecial 20 @llx 35
@lly 592 @urx 757 @ury 5720 @rwi @setspecial
%%BeginDocument: Figures/fullmin.1000.ps
150 dict begin gsave
/bd{bind def}def
/PVer 3200 def
% drawing commands
/I{Coord SetPage 1 setlinecap 1 setlinejoin
X    LineTypes{RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}forall
X    /Helvetica findfont
X    PointSize RastersPerPoint mul Cex mul scalefont setfont
X    /Colors GColors def
}bd
/BWOp{
X    bw{currentrgbcolor add add 2.9 gt{1}{0}ifelse setgray}if
X    exec
X    bw{CurSc Sc}if
}bd
/IBu{}def
/B{newpath}bd
/E{{stroke}BWOp}bd
/C{currentpoint Penup{newpath}{E}ifelse moveto}bd
/F{closepath eofill}bd
/M{moveto}bd
/L{lineto}bd
/Pu{load /XEQ exch def /Penup true def}bd
/Pd{/XEQ{}def /Penup false def}bd
/Px{currentdict /XEQ known{XEQ}if}bd
/h{Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/j{neg Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/k{exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/l{neg exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/m{moveto Penup{Px}if}bd
/x{0 Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/y{0 exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/w{neg x}bd
/z{neg y}bd
/a{B M dup y exch x neg y closepath}bd
/b{a eofill}bd
/c{a E}bd
/A{PageBegin BackCol 0 ge
X    {CurSc gsave 0 SC Page aload pop
X    exch 4 -1 roll dup 5 1 roll sub 3 1 roll exch dup 4 1 roll sub 4 2 roll b
X    grestore SC}if
}bd
/Ph{gsave Pch-x Pch-y rmoveto Show grestore}bd
/Pc{Pch Ph}bd
/T{/Adjust exch def gsave translate StringRot rotate 0 0 moveto
X    dup stringwidth pop neg Adjust mul 0 rmoveto
X    currentpoint translate TextShow grestore}bd
/X{erasepage InPage{PageEnd}if}bd
/Z{gsave showpage grestore PageEnd}bd
/W{grestore end}bd
% parameter setting commands
/saveAt{Attr begin
X    /Atlinewidth currentlinewidth def
X    /Atfont currentfont def
X    /Atdash currentdash 2 array astore def
X    /AtSc CurSc def
end}bd
/restAt{Attr begin
X    Atlinewidth Atfont Atdash AtSc
X    end
X    SC aload pop setdash setfont setlinewidth
}bd
/SC{dup dup 0 eq
X    {pop BackIdx
X        {BackCol dup 0 lt {pop 1 setgray} {Sc}ifelse}
X        {/Colors BColor def 1 Sc}ifelse}
X    {/Colors GColors def Sc}ifelse
X    /CurSc exch def
}bd
/St{1 sub LineTypes dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get 0 setdash}bd
/Sw{abs 2 div RastersPerPoint mul setlinewidth SetClip}bd
/Sp{dup 42 eq{pop IBu}{Pch exch 0 exch put SetPchSize}ifelse}bd
/Sx{dup Cex div /Ratio exch def
X     /Cex exch def
X     currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
X     /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
X     /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
X     /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sg{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Figure astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sr{/StringRot exch def}bd
/Sh{/CharRot exch def}bd
/Sd{0 eq /ClipToPlot exch def SetClip}bd
/Iv{/InPage false def/Clip 4 array def/Page 4 array def
X    /Figure [0 0 1 1] def/Plot [0 0 1 1] def/ClipToPlot true def
X    /Cex 1 def/Outline false def
X    /Pch 1 string def/Pch-x 0 def/Pch-y 0 def/Text-y 0 def
X    /LineTypes [ % in default units
X        [] [1 2] [4 4] [8 4] [13 3] [16 2 2 2] [8 2 2 2] [1 13] [6 5] [12 4]
X    ] def
X    /Attr 5 dict def/CurSc 1 def/Penup false def/XEQ{}def
}bd
/Rem{2 copy div floor mul sub floor cvi}bd
/RastersPerPoint{RastersPerInch 72 div}bd
/ScaleArray{/Factor exch def /Array exch def
X    0 1 Array length 1 sub
X    {dup Array exch get Factor mul Array 3 1 roll put}for}bd
/Coord{Region aload pop /uy exch def /ux exch def /ly exch def /lx exch def
X    uy ly sub ux lx sub Landscape{exch}if /Width exch def /Height exch def
X    lx ly translate Landscape{90 rotate 0 Height neg translate}if
X    1 RastersPerPoint div dup scale}bd
/SetPchSize{gsave
X    newpath 0 0 moveto Pch false charpath flattenpath pathbbox
X    exch 3 1 roll
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-y exch def
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-x exch def
X    grestore}bd
/Show{Outline{false charpath E}{{show}BWOp}ifelse}bd
/SimpleShow{0 Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto Show}bd
/FancyShow{
X    /RotDiff exch def
X    /Cos RotDiff cos abs def
X    /Sin RotDiff sin abs def
X    {
X        ( ) dup 0 4 -1 roll put
X        dup stringwidth pop /CharWidth exch def
X        Cos 0 eq{
X            Text-y Sin div
X        }{
X            Sin 0 eq{
X                CharWidth Cos div
X            }{
X                Text-y Sin div dup
X                CharWidth Cos div dup
X                4 1 roll lt{exch pop}{pop}ifelse
X            }ifelse
X        }ifelse 2 div /CharDist exch def
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X        gsave
X            RotDiff rotate
X            CharWidth 2 div neg Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto
X            Show
X        grestore
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X    }forall
}bd
/TextShow{
X    CharRot StringRot sub dup 0 eq{pop SimpleShow}{FancyShow}ifelse
}bd
/BoxClip{/CLW currentlinewidth def
X    2{CLW add 4 1 roll}repeat
X    2{CLW sub 4 1 roll}repeat
X    % initclip
X    saveAt grestore gsave restAt
X    newpath 2 index exch 2 index exch dup 6 index exch
X    moveto 3{lineto}repeat closepath clip newpath}bd
/Subregion{
X    7 dict begin/A exch def/Uy exch def/Ux exch def/Ly exch def/Lx exch def
X    Ux Lx sub A 0 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 1 get mul Ly add
X    Ux Lx sub A 2 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 3 get mul Ly add end}bd
/SetFigure{Page aload pop Figure Subregion}bd
/SetPlot{SetFigure Plot Subregion}bd
/SetClip{ClipToPlot{SetPlot}{SetFigure}ifelse BoxClip}bd
/SetPage{0 0 Width Height Page astore RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}bd
/PageBegin{save /PageContext exch def /InPage true def gsave}bd
/PageEnd{grestore PageContext restore /InPage false def}bd
/SImage{
X    dup /Bits exch def 8 exch idiv /PerByte exch def
X    /Ht exch def /Wid exch def
X    1 Wid div 1 Ht div scale
X    /saveSc CurSc def /Colors IColors def
X    /curstr Wid PerByte add 1 sub PerByte idiv string def
X    /MaskByte 16#ff Bits 8 sub bitshift def
X    1 1 Ht{
X        currentfile curstr readhexstring pop pop
X        /CurPos 0 def
X        /Left PerByte def
X        1 1 Wid{
X            Left PerByte eq{
X                /CurByte curstr CurPos get def
X                /MaskMove -8 Bits add def
X                /CurPos CurPos 1 add def
X            }if
X            CurByte MaskMove bitshift MaskByte and
X            dup 0 gt{
X                Sc
X                exch dup 3 1 roll B M 1 z 1 w 1 y F
X            }{pop pop}ifelse
X            Left 1 sub dup /Left exch def 0 le
X            {/Left PerByte def}
X            {/MaskMove MaskMove Bits add def}ifelse
X        }for
X        pop
X    }for
X    /Colors GColors def saveSc Sc
}bd
/Ic {} bd
/Sc {
X    dup dup 1 lt exch 0 ge and
X    {1 exch sub setgray}  % explicit gray level [0,1)
X    {1 sub Colors dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     dup type /arraytype eq {aload pop setrgbcolor} {setgray} ifelse
X    } ifelse
} bd
/If {} bd
/Sf {dup 0 lt /Outline exch def abs
X     1 sub Fonts dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     findfont PointSize Cex mul RastersPerPoint mul scalefont dup setfont
X     dup /FontMatrix get /Matrix exch def /FontBBox get aload pop
X     Matrix transform 4 2 roll Matrix transform
X     exch pop add /Text-y exch def pop SetPchSize} bd
% fixed controlling parameters
/Landscape true def
/Region [20.88 35.0886 591.12 756.911] def
/bw statusdict begin /processcolors where
{pop processcolors} {1} ifelse end 1 eq
X def
/RastersPerInch 300 def
/PointSize 14 def
/Fonts [
X	/Helvetica
X	/Courier
X	/Times-Roman
X	/Helvetica-Oblique
X	/Helvetica-Bold
X	/Helvetica-BoldOblique
X	/Courier-Oblique
X	/Courier-Bold
X	/Courier-BoldOblique
X	/Times-Italic
X	/Times-Bold
X	/Times-BoldItalic
X	/Symbol
X	/AvantGarde-Book
X	/AvantGarde-BookOblique
X	/AvantGarde-Demi
X	/AvantGarde-DemiOblique
X	/Bookman-Demi
X	/Bookman-DemiItalic
X	/Bookman-Light
X	/Bookman-LightItalic
X	/Helvetica-Narrow
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Bold
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-BoldOblique
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Oblique
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Roman
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Bold
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Italic
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-BoldItalic
X	/Palatino-Roman
X	/Palatino-Bold
X	/Palatino-Italic
X	/Palatino-BoldItalic
X	/ZapfChancery-MediumItalic
X	/ZapfDingbats
] def
/GColors [
X	0
X	0.6
X	0.3
X	0.9
X	0.4
X	0.7
X	0.1
X	0.5
X	0.8
X	0.2
] def
/BackIdx true def
/BackCol -1 def
/IColors [
X	0.933333
X	0.866667
X	0.8
X	0.733333
X	0.666667
X	0.6
X	0.533333
X	0.466667
X	0.4
X	0.333333
X	0.266667
X	0.2
X	0.133333
X	0.0666667
X	0
] def
/Colors GColors def
/IBu {Pch 0 8#267 put SetPchSize} def
/Bu {Pc} def
X
% all initialization action here
Iv I
currentdict /Ic known {Ic} if
currentdict /If known {If} if

%%BeginDocument: Figures/min.all.tried.ps
150 dict begin gsave
/bd{bind def}def
/PVer 3200 def
% drawing commands
/I{Coord SetPage 1 setlinecap 1 setlinejoin
X    LineTypes{RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}forall
X    /Helvetica findfont
X    PointSize RastersPerPoint mul Cex mul scalefont setfont
X    /Colors GColors def
}bd
/BWOp{
X    bw{currentrgbcolor add add 2.9 gt{1}{0}ifelse setgray}if
X    exec
X    bw{CurSc Sc}if
}bd
/IBu{}def
/B{newpath}bd
/E{{stroke}BWOp}bd
/C{currentpoint Penup{newpath}{E}ifelse moveto}bd
/F{closepath eofill}bd
/M{moveto}bd
/L{lineto}bd
/Pu{load /XEQ exch def /Penup true def}bd
/Pd{/XEQ{}def /Penup false def}bd
/Px{currentdict /XEQ known{XEQ}if}bd
/h{Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/j{neg Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/k{exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/l{neg exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/m{moveto Penup{Px}if}bd
/x{0 Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/y{0 exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/w{neg x}bd
/z{neg y}bd
/a{B M dup y exch x neg y closepath}bd
/b{a eofill}bd
/c{a E}bd
/A{PageBegin BackCol 0 ge
X    {CurSc gsave 0 SC Page aload pop
X    exch 4 -1 roll dup 5 1 roll sub 3 1 roll exch dup 4 1 roll sub 4 2 roll b
X    grestore SC}if
}bd
/Ph{gsave Pch-x Pch-y rmoveto Show grestore}bd
/Pc{Pch Ph}bd
/T{/Adjust exch def gsave translate StringRot rotate 0 0 moveto
X    dup stringwidth pop neg Adjust mul 0 rmoveto
X    currentpoint translate TextShow grestore}bd
/X{erasepage InPage{PageEnd}if}bd
/Z{gsave showpage grestore PageEnd}bd
/W{grestore end}bd
% parameter setting commands
/saveAt{Attr begin
X    /Atlinewidth currentlinewidth def
X    /Atfont currentfont def
X    /Atdash currentdash 2 array astore def
X    /AtSc CurSc def
end}bd
/restAt{Attr begin
X    Atlinewidth Atfont Atdash AtSc
X    end
X    SC aload pop setdash setfont setlinewidth
}bd
/SC{dup dup 0 eq
X    {pop BackIdx
X        {BackCol dup 0 lt {pop 1 setgray} {Sc}ifelse}
X        {/Colors BColor def 1 Sc}ifelse}
X    {/Colors GColors def Sc}ifelse
X    /CurSc exch def
}bd
/St{1 sub LineTypes dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get 0 setdash}bd
/Sw{abs 2 div RastersPerPoint mul setlinewidth SetClip}bd
/Sp{dup 42 eq{pop IBu}{Pch exch 0 exch put SetPchSize}ifelse}bd
/Sx{dup Cex div /Ratio exch def
X     /Cex exch def
X     currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
X     /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
X     /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
X     /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sg{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Figure astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sr{/StringRot exch def}bd
/Sh{/CharRot exch def}bd
/Sd{0 eq /ClipToPlot exch def SetClip}bd
/Iv{/InPage false def/Clip 4 array def/Page 4 array def
X    /Figure [0 0 1 1] def/Plot [0 0 1 1] def/ClipToPlot true def
X    /Cex 1 def/Outline false def
X    /Pch 1 string def/Pch-x 0 def/Pch-y 0 def/Text-y 0 def
X    /LineTypes [ % in default units
X        [] [1 2] [4 4] [8 4] [13 3] [16 2 2 2] [8 2 2 2] [1 13] [6 5] [12 4]
X    ] def
X    /Attr 5 dict def/CurSc 1 def/Penup false def/XEQ{}def
}bd
/Rem{2 copy div floor mul sub floor cvi}bd
/RastersPerPoint{RastersPerInch 72 div}bd
/ScaleArray{/Factor exch def /Array exch def
X    0 1 Array length 1 sub
X    {dup Array exch get Factor mul Array 3 1 roll put}for}bd
/Coord{Region aload pop /uy exch def /ux exch def /ly exch def /lx exch def
X    uy ly sub ux lx sub Landscape{exch}if /Width exch def /Height exch def
X    lx ly translate Landscape{90 rotate 0 Height neg translate}if
X    1 RastersPerPoint div dup scale}bd
/SetPchSize{gsave
X    newpath 0 0 moveto Pch false charpath flattenpath pathbbox
X    exch 3 1 roll
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-y exch def
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-x exch def
X    grestore}bd
/Show{Outline{false charpath E}{{show}BWOp}ifelse}bd
/SimpleShow{0 Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto Show}bd
/FancyShow{
X    /RotDiff exch def
X    /Cos RotDiff cos abs def
X    /Sin RotDiff sin abs def
X    {
X        ( ) dup 0 4 -1 roll put
X        dup stringwidth pop /CharWidth exch def
X        Cos 0 eq{
X            Text-y Sin div
X        }{
X            Sin 0 eq{
X                CharWidth Cos div
X            }{
X                Text-y Sin div dup
X                CharWidth Cos div dup
X                4 1 roll lt{exch pop}{pop}ifelse
X            }ifelse
X        }ifelse 2 div /CharDist exch def
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X        gsave
X            RotDiff rotate
X            CharWidth 2 div neg Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto
X            Show
X        grestore
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X    }forall
}bd
/TextShow{
X    CharRot StringRot sub dup 0 eq{pop SimpleShow}{FancyShow}ifelse
}bd
/BoxClip{/CLW currentlinewidth def
X    2{CLW add 4 1 roll}repeat
X    2{CLW sub 4 1 roll}repeat
X    % initclip
X    saveAt grestore gsave restAt
X    newpath 2 index exch 2 index exch dup 6 index exch
X    moveto 3{lineto}repeat closepath clip newpath}bd
/Subregion{
X    7 dict begin/A exch def/Uy exch def/Ux exch def/Ly exch def/Lx exch def
X    Ux Lx sub A 0 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 1 get mul Ly add
X    Ux Lx sub A 2 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 3 get mul Ly add end}bd
/SetFigure{Page aload pop Figure Subregion}bd
/SetPlot{SetFigure Plot Subregion}bd
/SetClip{ClipToPlot{SetPlot}{SetFigure}ifelse BoxClip}bd
/SetPage{0 0 Width Height Page astore RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}bd
/PageBegin{save /PageContext exch def /InPage true def gsave}bd
/PageEnd{grestore PageContext restore /InPage false def}bd
/SImage{
X    dup /Bits exch def 8 exch idiv /PerByte exch def
X    /Ht exch def /Wid exch def
X    1 Wid div 1 Ht div scale
X    /saveSc CurSc def /Colors IColors def
X    /curstr Wid PerByte add 1 sub PerByte idiv string def
X    /MaskByte 16#ff Bits 8 sub bitshift def
X    1 1 Ht{
X        currentfile curstr readhexstring pop pop
X        /CurPos 0 def
X        /Left PerByte def
X        1 1 Wid{
X            Left PerByte eq{
X                /CurByte curstr CurPos get def
X                /MaskMove -8 Bits add def
X                /CurPos CurPos 1 add def
X            }if
X            CurByte MaskMove bitshift MaskByte and
X            dup 0 gt{
X                Sc
X                exch dup 3 1 roll B M 1 z 1 w 1 y F
X            }{pop pop}ifelse
X            Left 1 sub dup /Left exch def 0 le
X            {/Left PerByte def}
X            {/MaskMove MaskMove Bits add def}ifelse
X        }for
X        pop
X    }for
X    /Colors GColors def saveSc Sc
}bd
/Ic {} bd
/Sc {
X    dup dup 1 lt exch 0 ge and
X    {1 exch sub setgray}  % explicit gray level [0,1)
X    {1 sub Colors dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     dup type /arraytype eq {aload pop setrgbcolor} {setgray} ifelse
X    } ifelse
} bd
/If {} bd
/Sf {dup 0 lt /Outline exch def abs
X     1 sub Fonts dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     findfont PointSize Cex mul RastersPerPoint mul scalefont dup setfont
X     dup /FontMatrix get /Matrix exch def /FontBBox get aload pop
X     Matrix transform 4 2 roll Matrix transform
X     exch pop add /Text-y exch def pop SetPchSize} bd
% fixed controlling parameters
/Landscape true def
/Region [20.88 35.0886 591.12 756.911] def
/bw statusdict begin /processcolors where
{pop processcolors} {1} ifelse end 1 eq
X def
/RastersPerInch 300 def
/PointSize 14 def
/Fonts [
X	/Helvetica
X	/Courier
X	/Times-Roman
X	/Helvetica-Oblique
X	/Helvetica-Bold
X	/Helvetica-BoldOblique
X	/Courier-Oblique
X	/Courier-Bold
X	/Courier-BoldOblique
X	/Times-Italic
X	/Times-Bold
X	/Times-BoldItalic
X	/Symbol
X	/AvantGarde-Book
X	/AvantGarde-BookOblique
X	/AvantGarde-Demi
X	/AvantGarde-DemiOblique
X	/Bookman-Demi
X	/Bookman-DemiItalic
X	/Bookman-Light
X	/Bookman-LightItalic
X	/Helvetica-Narrow
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Bold
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-BoldOblique
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Oblique
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Roman
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Bold
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Italic
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-BoldItalic
X	/Palatino-Roman
X	/Palatino-Bold
X	/Palatino-Italic
X	/Palatino-BoldItalic
X	/ZapfChancery-MediumItalic
X	/ZapfDingbats
] def
/GColors [
X	0
X	0.6
X	0.3
X	0.9
X	0.4
X	0.7
X	0.1
X	0.5
X	0.8
X	0.2
] def
/BackIdx true def
/BackCol -1 def
/IColors [
X	0.933333
X	0.866667
X	0.8

X	0
] def
/Colors GColors def
/IBu {Pch 0 8#267 put SetPchSize} def
/Bu {Pc} def

%%BeginDocument: Figures/min.gs.ps
150 dict begin gsave
/bd{bind def}def
/PVer 3200 def
% drawing commands
/I{Coord SetPage 1 setlinecap 1 setlinejoin
X    LineTypes{RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}forall
X    /Helvetica findfont
X    PointSize RastersPerPoint mul Cex mul scalefont setfont
X    /Colors GColors def
}bd
/BWOp{
X    bw{currentrgbcolor add add 2.9 gt{1}{0}ifelse setgray}if
X    exec
X    bw{CurSc Sc}if
}bd
/IBu{}def
/B{newpath}bd
/E{{stroke}BWOp}bd
/C{currentpoint Penup{newpath}{E}ifelse moveto}bd
/F{closepath eofill}bd
/M{moveto}bd
/L{lineto}bd
/Pu{load /XEQ exch def /Penup true def}bd
/Pd{/XEQ{}def /Penup false def}bd
/Px{currentdict /XEQ known{XEQ}if}bd
/h{Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/j{neg Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/k{exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/l{neg exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/m{moveto Penup{Px}if}bd
/x{0 Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/y{0 exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/w{neg x}bd
/z{neg y}bd
/a{B M dup y exch x neg y closepath}bd
/b{a eofill}bd
/c{a E}bd
/A{PageBegin BackCol 0 ge
X    {CurSc gsave 0 SC Page aload pop
X    exch 4 -1 roll dup 5 1 roll sub 3 1 roll exch dup 4 1 roll sub 4 2 roll b
X    grestore SC}if
}bd
/Ph{gsave Pch-x Pch-y rmoveto Show grestore}bd
/Pc{Pch Ph}bd
/T{/Adjust exch def gsave translate StringRot rotate 0 0 moveto
X    dup stringwidth pop neg Adjust mul 0 rmoveto
X    currentpoint translate TextShow grestore}bd
/X{erasepage InPage{PageEnd}if}bd
/Z{gsave showpage grestore PageEnd}bd
/W{grestore end}bd
% parameter setting commands
/saveAt{Attr begin
X    /Atlinewidth currentlinewidth def
X    /Atfont currentfont def
X    /Atdash currentdash 2 array astore def
X    /AtSc CurSc def
end}bd
/restAt{Attr begin
X    Atlinewidth Atfont Atdash AtSc
X    end
X    SC aload pop setdash setfont setlinewidth
}bd
/SC{dup dup 0 eq
X    {pop BackIdx
X        {BackCol dup 0 lt {pop 1 setgray} {Sc}ifelse}
X        {/Colors BColor def 1 Sc}ifelse}
X    {/Colors GColors def Sc}ifelse
X    /CurSc exch def
}bd
/St{1 sub LineTypes dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get 0 setdash}bd
/Sw{abs 2 div RastersPerPoint mul setlinewidth SetClip}bd
/Sp{dup 42 eq{pop IBu}{Pch exch 0 exch put SetPchSize}ifelse}bd
/Sx{dup Cex div /Ratio exch def
X     /Cex exch def
X     currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
X     /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
X     /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
X     /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sg{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Figure astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sr{/StringRot exch def}bd
/Sh{/CharRot exch def}bd
/Sd{0 eq /ClipToPlot exch def SetClip}bd
/Iv{/InPage false def/Clip 4 array def/Page 4 array def
X    /Figure [0 0 1 1] def/Plot [0 0 1 1] def/ClipToPlot true def
X    /Cex 1 def/Outline false def
X    /Pch 1 string def/Pch-x 0 def/Pch-y 0 def/Text-y 0 def
X    /LineTypes [ % in default units
X        [] [1 2] [4 4] [8 4] [13 3] [16 2 2 2] [8 2 2 2] [1 13] [6 5] [12 4]
X    ] def
X    /Attr 5 dict def/CurSc 1 def/Penup false def/XEQ{}def
}bd
/Rem{2 copy div floor mul sub floor cvi}bd
/RastersPerPoint{RastersPerInch 72 div}bd
/ScaleArray{/Factor exch def /Array exch def
X    0 1 Array length 1 sub
X    {dup Array exch get Factor mul Array 3 1 roll put}for}bd
/Coord{Region aload pop /uy exch def /ux exch def /ly exch def /lx exch def
X    uy ly sub ux lx sub Landscape{exch}if /Width exch def /Height exch def
X    lx ly translate Landscape{90 rotate 0 Height neg translate}if
X    1 RastersPerPoint div dup scale}bd
/SetPchSize{gsave
X    newpath 0 0 moveto Pch false charpath flattenpath pathbbox
X    exch 3 1 roll
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-y exch def
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-x exch def
X    grestore}bd
/Show{Outline{false charpath E}{{show}BWOp}ifelse}bd
/SimpleShow{0 Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto Show}bd
/FancyShow{
X    /RotDiff exch def
X    /Cos RotDiff cos abs def
X    /Sin RotDiff sin abs def
X    {
X        ( ) dup 0 4 -1 roll put
X        dup stringwidth pop /CharWidth exch def
X        Cos 0 eq{
X            Text-y Sin div
X        }{
X            Sin 0 eq{
X                CharWidth Cos div
X            }{
X                Text-y Sin div dup
X                CharWidth Cos div dup
X                4 1 roll lt{exch pop}{pop}ifelse
X            }ifelse
X        }ifelse 2 div /CharDist exch def
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X        gsave
X            RotDiff rotate
X            CharWidth 2 div neg Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto
X            Show
X        grestore
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X    }forall
}bd
/TextShow{
X    CharRot StringRot sub dup 0 eq{pop SimpleShow}{FancyShow}ifelse
}bd
/BoxClip{/CLW currentlinewidth def
X    2{CLW add 4 1 roll}repeat
X    2{CLW sub 4 1 roll}repeat
X    % initclip
X    saveAt grestore gsave restAt
X    newpath 2 index exch 2 index exch dup 6 index exch
X    moveto 3{lineto}repeat closepath clip newpath}bd
/Subregion{
X    7 dict begin/A exch def/Uy exch def/Ux exch def/Ly exch def/Lx exch def
X    Ux Lx sub A 0 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 1 get mul Ly add
X    Ux Lx sub A 2 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 3 get mul Ly add end}bd
/SetFigure{Page aload pop Figure Subregion}bd
/SetPlot{SetFigure Plot Subregion}bd
/SetClip{ClipToPlot{SetPlot}{SetFigure}ifelse BoxClip}bd
/SetPage{0 0 Width Height Page astore RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}bd
/PageBegin{save /PageContext exch def /InPage true def gsave}bd
/PageEnd{grestore PageContext restore /InPage false def}bd
/SImage{
X    dup /Bits exch def 8 exch idiv /PerByte exch def
X    /Ht exch def /Wid exch def
X    1 Wid div 1 Ht div scale
X    /saveSc CurSc def /Colors IColors def
X    /curstr Wid PerByte add 1 sub PerByte idiv string def
X    /MaskByte 16#ff Bits 8 sub bitshift def
X    1 1 Ht{
X        currentfile curstr readhexstring pop pop
X        /CurPos 0 def
X        /Left PerByte def
X        1 1 Wid{
X            Left PerByte eq{
X                /CurByte curstr CurPos get def
X                /MaskMove -8 Bits add def
X                /CurPos CurPos 1 add def
X            }if
X            CurByte MaskMove bitshift MaskByte and
X            dup 0 gt{
X                Sc
X                exch dup 3 1 roll B M 1 z 1 w 1 y F
X            }{pop pop}ifelse
X            Left 1 sub dup /Left exch def 0 le
X            {/Left PerByte def}
X            {/MaskMove MaskMove Bits add def}ifelse
X        }for
X        pop
X    }for
X    /Colors GColors def saveSc Sc
}bd
/Ic {} bd
/Sc {
X    dup dup 1 lt exch 0 ge and
X    {1 exch sub setgray}  % explicit gray level [0,1)
X    {1 sub Colors dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     dup type /arraytype eq {aload pop setrgbcolor} {setgray} ifelse
X    } ifelse
} bd
/If {} bd
/Sf {dup 0 lt /Outline exch def abs
X     1 sub Fonts dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     findfont PointSize Cex mul RastersPerPoint mul scalefont dup setfont
X     dup /FontMatrix get /Matrix exch def /FontBBox get aload pop
X     Matrix transform 4 2 roll Matrix transform
X     exch pop add /Text-y exch def pop SetPchSize} bd
% fixed controlling parameters
/Landscape true def
/Region [20.88 35.0886 591.12 756.911] def
/bw statusdict begin /processcolors where
{pop processcolors} {1} ifelse end 1 eq
X def

neg exch translate
X 1390 1863 a 1390 1863 a
X gsave currentpoint currentpoint translate 270 neg rotate neg exch
neg exch translate
X 1390 1863 a @beginspecial
20 @llx 35 @lly 592 @urx 757 @ury 5720 @rwi @setspecial
%%BeginDocument: Figures/min.gs+br.ps
150 dict begin gsave
/bd{bind def}def
/PVer 3200 def
% drawing commands
/I{Coord SetPage 1 setlinecap 1 setlinejoin
X    LineTypes{RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}forall
X    /Helvetica findfont
X    PointSize RastersPerPoint mul Cex mul scalefont setfont
X    /Colors GColors def
}bd
/BWOp{
X    bw{currentrgbcolor add add 2.9 gt{1}{0}ifelse setgray}if
X    exec
X    bw{CurSc Sc}if
}bd
/IBu{}def
/B{newpath}bd
/E{{stroke}BWOp}bd
/C{currentpoint Penup{newpath}{E}ifelse moveto}bd
/F{closepath eofill}bd
/M{moveto}bd
/L{lineto}bd
/Pu{load /XEQ exch def /Penup true def}bd
/Pd{/XEQ{}def /Penup false def}bd
/Px{currentdict /XEQ known{XEQ}if}bd
/h{Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/j{neg Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/k{exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/l{neg exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/m{moveto Penup{Px}if}bd
/x{0 Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/y{0 exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/w{neg x}bd
/z{neg y}bd
/a{B M dup y exch x neg y closepath}bd
/b{a eofill}bd
/c{a E}bd
/A{PageBegin BackCol 0 ge
X    {CurSc gsave 0 SC Page aload pop
X    exch 4 -1 roll dup 5 1 roll sub 3 1 roll exch dup 4 1 roll sub 4 2 roll b
X    grestore SC}if
}bd
/Ph{gsave Pch-x Pch-y rmoveto Show grestore}bd
/Pc{Pch Ph}bd
/T{/Adjust exch def gsave translate StringRot rotate 0 0 moveto
X    dup stringwidth pop neg Adjust mul 0 rmoveto
X    currentpoint translate TextShow grestore}bd
/X{erasepage InPage{PageEnd}if}bd
/Z{gsave showpage grestore PageEnd}bd
/W{grestore end}bd
% parameter setting commands
/saveAt{Attr begin
X    /Atlinewidth currentlinewidth def
X    /Atfont currentfont def
X    /Atdash currentdash 2 array astore def
X    /AtSc CurSc def
end}bd
/restAt{Attr begin
X    Atlinewidth Atfont Atdash AtSc
X    end
X    SC aload pop setdash setfont setlinewidth
}bd
/SC{dup dup 0 eq
X    {pop BackIdx
X        {BackCol dup 0 lt {pop 1 setgray} {Sc}ifelse}
X        {/Colors BColor def 1 Sc}ifelse}
X    {/Colors GColors def Sc}ifelse
X    /CurSc exch def
}bd
/St{1 sub LineTypes dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get 0 setdash}bd
/Sw{abs 2 div RastersPerPoint mul setlinewidth SetClip}bd
/Sp{dup 42 eq{pop IBu}{Pch exch 0 exch put SetPchSize}ifelse}bd
/Sx{dup Cex div /Ratio exch def
X     /Cex exch def
X     currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
X     /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
X     /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
X     /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sg{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Figure astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sr{/StringRot exch def}bd
/Sh{/CharRot exch def}bd
/Sd{0 eq /ClipToPlot exch def SetClip}bd
/Iv{/InPage false def/Clip 4 array def/Page 4 array def
X    /Figure [0 0 1 1] def/Plot [0 0 1 1] def/ClipToPlot true def
X    /Cex 1 def/Outline false def
X    /Pch 1 string def/Pch-x 0 def/Pch-y 0 def/Text-y 0 def
X    /LineTypes [ % in default units
X        [] [1 2] [4 4] [8 4] [13 3] [16 2 2 2] [8 2 2 2] [1 13] [6 5] [12 4]
X    ] def
X    /Attr 5 dict def/CurSc 1 def/Penup false def/XEQ{}def
}bd
/Rem{2 copy div floor mul sub floor cvi}bd
/RastersPerPoint{RastersPerInch 72 div}bd
/ScaleArray{/Factor exch def /Array exch def
X    0 1 Array length 1 sub
X    {dup Array exch get Factor mul Array 3 1 roll put}for}bd
/Coord{Region aload pop /uy exch def /ux exch def /ly exch def /lx exch def
X    uy ly sub ux lx sub Landscape{exch}if /Width exch def /Height exch def
X    lx ly translate Landscape{90 rotate 0 Height neg translate}if
X    1 RastersPerPoint div dup scale}bd
/SetPchSize{gsave
X    newpath 0 0 moveto Pch false charpath flattenpath pathbbox
X    exch 3 1 roll
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-y exch def
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-x exch def
X    grestore}bd
/Show{Outline{false charpath E}{{show}BWOp}ifelse}bd
/SimpleShow{0 Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto Show}bd
/FancyShow{
X    /RotDiff exch def
X    /Cos RotDiff cos abs def
X    /Sin RotDiff sin abs def
X    {
X        ( ) dup 0 4 -1 roll put
X        dup stringwidth pop /CharWidth exch def
X        Cos 0 eq{
X            Text-y Sin div
X        }{
X            Sin 0 eq{
X                CharWidth Cos div
X            }{
X                Text-y Sin div dup
X                CharWidth Cos div dup
X                4 1 roll lt{exch pop}{pop}ifelse
X            }ifelse
X        }ifelse 2 div /CharDist exch def
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X        gsave
X            RotDiff rotate
X            CharWidth 2 div neg Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto
X            Show
X        grestore
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X    }forall
}bd
/TextShow{
X    CharRot StringRot sub dup 0 eq{pop SimpleShow}{FancyShow}ifelse
}bd
/BoxClip{/CLW currentlinewidth def
X    2{CLW add 4 1 roll}repeat
X    2{CLW sub 4 1 roll}repeat
X    % initclip
X    saveAt grestore gsave restAt
X    newpath 2 index exch 2 index exch dup 6 index exch
X    moveto 3{lineto}repeat closepath clip newpath}bd
/Subregion{
X    7 dict begin/A exch def/Uy exch def/Ux exch def/Ly exch def/Lx exch def
X    Ux Lx sub A 0 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 1 get mul Ly add
X    Ux Lx sub A 2 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 3 get mul Ly add end}bd
/SetFigure{Page aload pop Figure Subregion}bd
/SetPlot{SetFigure Plot Subregion}bd
/SetClip{ClipToPlot{SetPlot}{SetFigure}ifelse BoxClip}bd
/SetPage{0 0 Width Height Page astore RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}bd
/PageBegin{save /PageContext exch def /InPage true def gsave}bd
/PageEnd{grestore PageContext restore /InPage false def}bd
/SImage{
X    dup /Bits exch def 8 exch idiv /PerByte exch def
X    /Ht exch def /Wid exch def
X    1 Wid div 1 Ht div scale
X    /saveSc CurSc def /Colors IColors def
X    /curstr Wid PerByte add 1 sub PerByte idiv string def
X    /MaskByte 16#ff Bits 8 sub bitshift def
X    1 1 Ht{
X        currentfile curstr readhexstring pop pop
X        /CurPos 0 def
X        /Left PerByte def
X        1 1 Wid{
X            Left PerByte eq{
X                /CurByte curstr CurPos get def
X                /MaskMove -8 Bits add def
X                /CurPos CurPos 1 add def
X            }if
X            CurByte MaskMove bitshift MaskByte and
X            dup 0 gt{
X                Sc
X                exch dup 3 1 roll B M 1 z 1 w 1 y F
X            }{pop pop}ifelse
X            Left 1 sub dup /Left exch def 0 le
X            {/Left PerByte def}
X            {/MaskMove MaskMove Bits add def}ifelse
X        }for
X        pop
X    }for
X    /Colors GColors def saveSc Sc
}bd
/Ic {} bd
/Sc {
X    dup dup 1 lt exch 0 ge and
X    {1 exch sub setgray}  % explicit gray level [0,1)
X    {1 sub Colors dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     dup type /arraytype eq {aload pop setrgbcolor} {setgray} ifelse
X    } ifelse
} bd
/If {} bd
/Sf {dup 0 lt /Outline exch def abs
X     1 sub Fonts dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     findfont PointSize Cex mul RastersPerPoint mul scalefont dup setfont
X     dup /FontMatrix get /Matrix exch def /FontBBox get aload pop
X     Matrix transform 4 2 roll Matrix transform
X     exch pop add /Text-y exch def pop SetPchSize} bd
% fixed controlling parameters
/Landscape true def
/Region [20.88 35.0886 591.12 756.911] def
/bw statusdict begin /processcolors where
{pop processcolors} {1} ifelse end 1 eq
X def
/RastersPerInch 300 def
/PointSize 14 def

%%BeginDocument: Figures/figure.motcyc1a.ps
150 dict begin gsave
/bd{bind def}def
/PVer 3200 def
% drawing commands
/I{Coord SetPage 1 setlinecap 1 setlinejoin
X    LineTypes{RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}forall
X    /Helvetica findfont
X    PointSize RastersPerPoint mul Cex mul scalefont setfont
X    /Colors GColors def
}bd
/BWOp{
X    bw{currentrgbcolor add add 2.9 gt{1}{0}ifelse setgray}if
X    exec
X    bw{CurSc Sc}if
}bd
/IBu{}def
/B{newpath}bd
/E{{stroke}BWOp}bd
/C{currentpoint Penup{newpath}{E}ifelse moveto}bd
/F{closepath eofill}bd
/M{moveto}bd
/L{lineto}bd
/Pu{load /XEQ exch def /Penup true def}bd
/Pd{/XEQ{}def /Penup false def}bd
/Px{currentdict /XEQ known{XEQ}if}bd
/h{Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/j{neg Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/k{exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/l{neg exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/m{moveto Penup{Px}if}bd
/x{0 Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/y{0 exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/w{neg x}bd
/z{neg y}bd
/a{B M dup y exch x neg y closepath}bd
/b{a eofill}bd
/c{a E}bd
/A{PageBegin BackCol 0 ge
X    {CurSc gsave 0 SC Page aload pop
X    exch 4 -1 roll dup 5 1 roll sub 3 1 roll exch dup 4 1 roll sub 4 2 roll b
X    grestore SC}if
}bd
/Ph{gsave Pch-x Pch-y rmoveto Show grestore}bd
/Pc{Pch Ph}bd
/T{/Adjust exch def gsave translate StringRot rotate 0 0 moveto
X    dup stringwidth pop neg Adjust mul 0 rmoveto
X    currentpoint translate TextShow grestore}bd
/X{erasepage InPage{PageEnd}if}bd
/Z{gsave showpage grestore PageEnd}bd
/W{grestore end}bd
% parameter setting commands
/saveAt{Attr begin
X    /Atlinewidth currentlinewidth def
X    /Atfont currentfont def
X    /Atdash currentdash 2 array astore def
X    /AtSc CurSc def
end}bd
/restAt{Attr begin
X    Atlinewidth Atfont Atdash AtSc
X    end
X    SC aload pop setdash setfont setlinewidth
}bd
/SC{dup dup 0 eq
X    {pop BackIdx
X        {BackCol dup 0 lt {pop 1 setgray} {Sc}ifelse}
X        {/Colors BColor def 1 Sc}ifelse}
X    {/Colors GColors def Sc}ifelse
X    /CurSc exch def
}bd
/St{1 sub LineTypes dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get 0 setdash}bd
/Sw{abs 2 div RastersPerPoint mul setlinewidth SetClip}bd
/Sp{dup 42 eq{pop IBu}{Pch exch 0 exch put SetPchSize}ifelse}bd
/Sx{dup Cex div /Ratio exch def
X     /Cex exch def
X     currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
X     /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
X     /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
X     /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sg{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Figure astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sr{/StringRot exch def}bd
/Sh{/CharRot exch def}bd
/Sd{0 eq /ClipToPlot exch def SetClip}bd
/Iv{/InPage false def/Clip 4 array def/Page 4 array def
X    /Figure [0 0 1 1] def/Plot [0 0 1 1] def/ClipToPlot true def
X    /Cex 1 def/Outline false def
X    /Pch 1 string def/Pch-x 0 def/Pch-y 0 def/Text-y 0 def
X    /LineTypes [ % in default units
X        [] [1 2] [4 4] [8 4] [13 3] [16 2 2 2] [8 2 2 2] [1 13] [6 5] [12 4]
X    ] def
X    /Attr 5 dict def/CurSc 1 def/Penup false def/XEQ{}def
}bd
/Rem{2 copy div floor mul sub floor cvi}bd
/RastersPerPoint{RastersPerInch 72 div}bd
/ScaleArray{/Factor exch def /Array exch def
X    0 1 Array length 1 sub
X    {dup Array exch get Factor mul Array 3 1 roll put}for}bd
/Coord{Region aload pop /uy exch def /ux exch def /ly exch def /lx exch def
X    uy ly sub ux lx sub Landscape{exch}if /Width exch def /Height exch def
X    lx ly translate Landscape{90 rotate 0 Height neg translate}if
X    1 RastersPerPoint div dup scale}bd
/SetPchSize{gsave
X    newpath 0 0 moveto Pch false charpath flattenpath pathbbox
X    exch 3 1 roll
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-y exch def
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-x exch def
X    grestore}bd
/Show{Outline{false charpath E}{{show}BWOp}ifelse}bd
/SimpleShow{0 Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto Show}bd
/FancyShow{
X    /RotDiff exch def
X    /Cos RotDiff cos abs def
X    /Sin RotDiff sin abs def
X    {
X        ( ) dup 0 4 -1 roll put
X        dup stringwidth pop /CharWidth exch def
X        Cos 0 eq{
X            Text-y Sin div
X        }{
X            Sin 0 eq{
X                CharWidth Cos div
X            }{
X                Text-y Sin div dup
X                CharWidth Cos div dup
X                4 1 roll lt{exch pop}{pop}ifelse
X            }ifelse
X        }ifelse 2 div /CharDist exch def
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X        gsave
X            RotDiff rotate
X            CharWidth 2 div neg Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto
X            Show
X        grestore
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X    }forall
}bd
/TextShow{
X    CharRot StringRot sub dup 0 eq{pop SimpleShow}{FancyShow}ifelse
}bd
/BoxClip{/CLW currentlinewidth def
X    2{CLW add 4 1 roll}repeat
X    2{CLW sub 4 1 roll}repeat
X    % initclip
X    saveAt grestore gsave restAt
X    newpath 2 index exch 2 index exch dup 6 index exch
X    moveto 3{lineto}repeat closepath clip newpath}bd
/Subregion{
X    7 dict begin/A exch def/Uy exch def/Ux exch def/Ly exch def/Lx exch def
X    Ux Lx sub A 0 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 1 get mul Ly add
X    Ux Lx sub A 2 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 3 get mul Ly add end}bd
/SetFigure{Page aload pop Figure Subregion}bd
/SetPlot{SetFigure Plot Subregion}bd
/SetClip{ClipToPlot{SetPlot}{SetFigure}ifelse BoxClip}bd
/SetPage{0 0 Width Height Page astore RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}bd
/PageBegin{save /PageContext exch def /InPage true def gsave}bd
/PageEnd{grestore PageContext restore /InPage false def}bd
/SImage{
X    dup /Bits exch def 8 exch idiv /PerByte exch def
X    /Ht exch def /Wid exch def
X    1 Wid div 1 Ht div scale
X    /saveSc CurSc def /Colors IColors def
X    /curstr Wid PerByte add 1 sub PerByte idiv string def
X    /MaskByte 16#ff Bits 8 sub bitshift def
X    1 1 Ht{
X        currentfile curstr readhexstring pop pop
X        /CurPos 0 def
X        /Left PerByte def
X        1 1 Wid{
X            Left PerByte eq{
X                /CurByte curstr CurPos get def
X                /MaskMove -8 Bits add def
X                /CurPos CurPos 1 add def
X            }if
X            CurByte MaskMove bitshift MaskByte and
X            dup 0 gt{
X                Sc
X                exch dup 3 1 roll B M 1 z 1 w 1 y F
X            }{pop pop}ifelse
X            Left 1 sub dup /Left exch def 0 le
X            {/Left PerByte def}
X            {/MaskMove MaskMove Bits add def}ifelse
X        }for
X        pop
X    }for
X    /Colors GColors def saveSc Sc
}bd
/Ic {} bd
/Sc {
X    dup dup 1 lt exch 0 ge and
X    {1 exch sub setgray}  % explicit gray level [0,1)
X    {1 sub Colors dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     dup type /arraytype eq {aload pop setrgbcolor} {setgray} ifelse
X    } ifelse
} bd
/If {} bd
/Sf {dup 0 lt /Outline exch def abs
X     1 sub Fonts dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     findfont PointSize Cex mul RastersPerPoint mul scalefont dup setfont
X     dup /FontMatrix get /Matrix exch def /FontBBox get aload pop
X     Matrix transform 4 2 roll Matrix transform
X     exch pop add /Text-y exch def pop SetPchSize} bd
% fixed controlling parameters
/Landscape true def
/Region [20.88 35.0886 591.12 756.911] def
/bw statusdict begin /processcolors where
{pop processcolors} {1} ifelse end 1 eq
X def
/RastersPerInch 300 def
/PointSize 14 def
/Fonts [
X	/Helvetica
X	/Courier
X	/Times-Roman
X	/Helvetica-Oblique
X	/Helvetica-Bold
X	/Helvetica-BoldOblique
X	/Courier-Oblique
X	/Courier-Bold
X	/Courier-BoldOblique
X	/Times-Italic
X	/Times-Bold
X	/Times-BoldItalic
X	/Symbol
X	/AvantGarde-Book
X	/AvantGarde-BookOblique
X	/AvantGarde-Demi
X	/AvantGarde-DemiOblique
X	/Bookman-Demi
X	/Bookman-DemiItalic
X	/Bookman-Light
X	/Bookman-LightItalic
X	/Helvetica-Narrow
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Bold
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-BoldOblique
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Oblique
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Roman
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Bold
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Italic
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-BoldItalic
X	/Palatino-Roman
X	/Palatino-Bold
X	/Palatino-Italic
X	/Palatino-BoldItalic
X	/ZapfChancery-MediumItalic
X	/ZapfDingbats
] def
/GColors [
X	0
X	0.6
X	0.3
X	0.9
X	0.4
X	0.7
X	0.1
X	0.5
X	0.8
X	0.2
] def
/BackIdx true def
/BackCol -1 def
/IColors [
X	0.933333
X	0.866667
X	0.8
X	0.733333
X	0.666667
X	0.6
X	0.533333
X	0.466667
X	0.4
X	0.333333
X	0.266667
X	0.2
X	0.133333
X	0.0666667
X	0
] def
/Colors GColors def
/IBu {Pch 0 8#267 put SetPchSize} def
/Bu {Pc} def
X
% all initialization action here
Iv I
currentdict /Ic known {Ic} if
currentdict /If known {If} if

%%BeginDocument: Figures/figure.motcyc2a.ps
150 dict begin gsave
/bd{bind def}def
/PVer 3200 def
% drawing commands
/I{Coord SetPage 1 setlinecap 1 setlinejoin
X    LineTypes{RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}forall
X    /Helvetica findfont
X    PointSize RastersPerPoint mul Cex mul scalefont setfont
X    /Colors GColors def
}bd
/BWOp{
X    bw{currentrgbcolor add add 2.9 gt{1}{0}ifelse setgray}if
X    exec
X    bw{CurSc Sc}if
}bd
/IBu{}def
/B{newpath}bd
/E{{stroke}BWOp}bd
/C{currentpoint Penup{newpath}{E}ifelse moveto}bd
/F{closepath eofill}bd
/M{moveto}bd
/L{lineto}bd
/Pu{load /XEQ exch def /Penup true def}bd
/Pd{/XEQ{}def /Penup false def}bd
/Px{currentdict /XEQ known{XEQ}if}bd
/h{Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/j{neg Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/k{exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/l{neg exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/m{moveto Penup{Px}if}bd
/x{0 Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/y{0 exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/w{neg x}bd
/z{neg y}bd
/a{B M dup y exch x neg y closepath}bd
/b{a eofill}bd
/c{a E}bd
/A{PageBegin BackCol 0 ge
X    {CurSc gsave 0 SC Page aload pop
X    exch 4 -1 roll dup 5 1 roll sub 3 1 roll exch dup 4 1 roll sub 4 2 roll b
X    grestore SC}if
}bd
/Ph{gsave Pch-x Pch-y rmoveto Show grestore}bd
/Pc{Pch Ph}bd

X    dup stringwidth pop neg Adjust mul 0 rmoveto

/W{grestore end}bd
% parameter setting commands
/saveAt{Attr begin
X    /Atlinewidth currentlinewidth def

X    /Atdash currentdash 2 array astore def
X    /AtSc CurSc def
end}bd
/restAt{Attr begin
X    Atlinewidth Atfont Atdash AtSc
X    end
X    SC aload pop setdash setfont setlinewidth
}bd
/SC{dup dup 0 eq
X    {pop BackIdx
X        {BackCol dup 0 lt {pop 1 setgray} {Sc}ifelse}
X        {/Colors BColor def 1 Sc}ifelse}
X    {/Colors GColors def Sc}ifelse

}bd

X     /Cex exch def
X     currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
X     /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
X     /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
X     /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sg{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Figure astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sr{/StringRot exch def}bd
/Sh{/CharRot exch def}bd

/Iv{/InPage false def/Clip 4 array def/Page 4 array def
X    /Figure [0 0 1 1] def/Plot [0 0 1 1] def/ClipToPlot true def

X    /LineTypes [ % in default units
X        [] [1 2] [4 4] [8 4] [13 3] [16 2 2 2] [8 2 2 2] [1 13] [6 5] [12 4]
X    ] def
X    /Attr 5 dict def/CurSc 1 def/Penup false def/XEQ{}def
}bd
/Rem{2 copy div floor mul sub floor cvi}bd

X    0 1 Array length 1 sub

/SetPchSize{gsave

X    add 2 div neg /Pch-x exch def
X    grestore}bd
/Show{Outline{false charpath E}{{show}BWOp}ifelse}bd
/SimpleShow{0 Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto Show}bd
/FancyShow{
X    /RotDiff exch def
X    /Cos RotDiff cos abs def
X    /Sin RotDiff sin abs def
X    {
X        ( ) dup 0 4 -1 roll put
X        dup stringwidth pop /CharWidth exch def
X        Cos 0 eq{
X            Text-y Sin div
X        }{
X            Sin 0 eq{
X                CharWidth Cos div
X            }{
X                Text-y Sin div dup
X                CharWidth Cos div dup
X                4 1 roll lt{exch pop}{pop}ifelse
X            }ifelse
X        }ifelse 2 div /CharDist exch def
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X        gsave
X            RotDiff rotate
X            CharWidth 2 div neg Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto
X            Show
X        grestore
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X    }forall
}bd
/TextShow{
X    CharRot StringRot sub dup 0 eq{pop SimpleShow}{FancyShow}ifelse
}bd
/BoxClip{/CLW currentlinewidth def
X    2{CLW add 4 1 roll}repeat
X    2{CLW sub 4 1 roll}repeat
X    % initclip
X    saveAt grestore gsave restAt
X    newpath 2 index exch 2 index exch dup 6 index exch
X    moveto 3{lineto}repeat closepath clip newpath}bd
/Subregion{
X    7 dict begin/A exch def/Uy exch def/Ux exch def/Ly exch def/Lx exch def
X    Ux Lx sub A 0 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 1 get mul Ly add
X    Ux Lx sub A 2 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 3 get mul Ly add end}bd
/SetFigure{Page aload pop Figure Subregion}bd
/SetPlot{SetFigure Plot Subregion}bd
/SetClip{ClipToPlot{SetPlot}{SetFigure}ifelse BoxClip}bd
/SetPage{0 0 Width Height Page astore RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}bd
/PageBegin{save /PageContext exch def /InPage true def gsave}bd
/PageEnd{grestore PageContext restore /InPage false def}bd
/SImage{
X    dup /Bits exch def 8 exch idiv /PerByte exch def
X    /Ht exch def /Wid exch def
X    1 Wid div 1 Ht div scale
X    /saveSc CurSc def /Colors IColors def
X    /curstr Wid PerByte add 1 sub PerByte idiv string def
X    /MaskByte 16#ff Bits 8 sub bitshift def
X    1 1 Ht{
X        currentfile curstr readhexstring pop pop
X        /CurPos 0 def
X        /Left PerByte def
X        1 1 Wid{
X            Left PerByte eq{
X                /CurByte curstr CurPos get def
X                /MaskMove -8 Bits add def
X                /CurPos CurPos 1 add def
X            }if
X            CurByte MaskMove bitshift MaskByte and
X            dup 0 gt{
X                Sc
X                exch dup 3 1 roll B M 1 z 1 w 1 y F
X            }{pop pop}ifelse
X            Left 1 sub dup /Left exch def 0 le
X            {/Left PerByte def}
X            {/MaskMove MaskMove Bits add def}ifelse
X        }for
X        pop
X    }for
X    /Colors GColors def saveSc Sc
}bd
/Ic {} bd
/Sc {
X    dup dup 1 lt exch 0 ge and
X    {1 exch sub setgray}  % explicit gray level [0,1)
X    {1 sub Colors dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     dup type /arraytype eq {aload pop setrgbcolor} {setgray} ifelse
X    } ifelse
} bd
/If {} bd
/Sf {dup 0 lt /Outline exch def abs
X     1 sub Fonts dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     findfont PointSize Cex mul RastersPerPoint mul scalefont dup setfont
X     dup /FontMatrix get /Matrix exch def /FontBBox get aload pop
X     Matrix transform 4 2 roll Matrix transform
X     exch pop add /Text-y exch def pop SetPchSize} bd
% fixed controlling parameters
/Landscape true def
/Region [20.88 35.0886 591.12 756.911] def
/bw statusdict begin /processcolors where
{pop processcolors} {1} ifelse end 1 eq
X def
/RastersPerInch 300 def
/PointSize 14 def
/Fonts [
X	/Helvetica
X	/Courier
X	/Times-Roman
X	/Helvetica-Oblique
X	/Helvetica-Bold
X	/Helvetica-BoldOblique
X	/Courier-Oblique
X	/Courier-Bold
X	/Courier-BoldOblique
X	/Times-Italic
X	/Times-Bold
X	/Times-BoldItalic
X	/Symbol
X	/AvantGarde-Book
X	/AvantGarde-BookOblique
X	/AvantGarde-Demi
X	/AvantGarde-DemiOblique
X	/Bookman-Demi
X	/Bookman-DemiItalic
X	/Bookman-Light
X	/Bookman-LightItalic
X	/Helvetica-Narrow
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Bold
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-BoldOblique
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Oblique
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Roman
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Bold
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-Italic
X	/NewCenturySchlbk-BoldItalic
X	/Palatino-Roman
X	/Palatino-Bold
X	/Palatino-Italic
X	/Palatino-BoldItalic
X	/ZapfChancery-MediumItalic
X	/ZapfDingbats
] def
/GColors [
X	0
X	0.6
X	0.3
X	0.9
X	0.4
X	0.7
X	0.1
X	0.5
X	0.8
X	0.2
] def
/BackIdx true def
/BackCol -1 def
/IColors [
X	0.933333

%%BeginDocument: Figures/figure.motcyc1b.ps
150 dict begin gsave
/bd{bind def}def
/PVer 3200 def
% drawing commands
/I{Coord SetPage 1 setlinecap 1 setlinejoin
X    LineTypes{RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}forall
X    /Helvetica findfont
X    PointSize RastersPerPoint mul Cex mul scalefont setfont
X    /Colors GColors def
}bd
/BWOp{
X    bw{currentrgbcolor add add 2.9 gt{1}{0}ifelse setgray}if
X    exec
X    bw{CurSc Sc}if
}bd
/IBu{}def
/B{newpath}bd
/E{{stroke}BWOp}bd
/C{currentpoint Penup{newpath}{E}ifelse moveto}bd
/F{closepath eofill}bd
/M{moveto}bd
/L{lineto}bd
/Pu{load /XEQ exch def /Penup true def}bd
/Pd{/XEQ{}def /Penup false def}bd
/Px{currentdict /XEQ known{XEQ}if}bd
/h{Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/j{neg Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/k{exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/l{neg exch neg exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/m{moveto Penup{Px}if}bd
/x{0 Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/y{0 exch Penup{rmoveto Px}{rlineto}ifelse}bd
/w{neg x}bd
/z{neg y}bd
/a{B M dup y exch x neg y closepath}bd
/b{a eofill}bd
/c{a E}bd
/A{PageBegin BackCol 0 ge
X    {CurSc gsave 0 SC Page aload pop
X    exch 4 -1 roll dup 5 1 roll sub 3 1 roll exch dup 4 1 roll sub 4 2 roll b
X    grestore SC}if
}bd
/Ph{gsave Pch-x Pch-y rmoveto Show grestore}bd
/Pc{Pch Ph}bd
/T{/Adjust exch def gsave translate StringRot rotate 0 0 moveto
X    dup stringwidth pop neg Adjust mul 0 rmoveto
X    currentpoint translate TextShow grestore}bd
/X{erasepage InPage{PageEnd}if}bd
/Z{gsave showpage grestore PageEnd}bd
/W{grestore end}bd
% parameter setting commands
/saveAt{Attr begin
X    /Atlinewidth currentlinewidth def
X    /Atfont currentfont def
X    /Atdash currentdash 2 array astore def
X    /AtSc CurSc def
end}bd
/restAt{Attr begin
X    Atlinewidth Atfont Atdash AtSc
X    end
X    SC aload pop setdash setfont setlinewidth
}bd
/SC{dup dup 0 eq
X    {pop BackIdx
X        {BackCol dup 0 lt {pop 1 setgray} {Sc}ifelse}
X        {/Colors BColor def 1 Sc}ifelse}
X    {/Colors GColors def Sc}ifelse
X    /CurSc exch def
}bd
/St{1 sub LineTypes dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get 0 setdash}bd
/Sw{abs 2 div RastersPerPoint mul setlinewidth SetClip}bd
/Sp{dup 42 eq{pop IBu}{Pch exch 0 exch put SetPchSize}ifelse}bd
/Sx{dup Cex div /Ratio exch def
X     /Cex exch def
X     currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
X     /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
X     /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
X     /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sg{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Figure astore pop SetClip}bd
/Sr{/StringRot exch def}bd
/Sh{/CharRot exch def}bd
/Sd{0 eq /ClipToPlot exch def SetClip}bd
/Iv{/InPage false def/Clip 4 array def/Page 4 array def
X    /Figure [0 0 1 1] def/Plot [0 0 1 1] def/ClipToPlot true def
X    /Cex 1 def/Outline false def
X    /Pch 1 string def/Pch-x 0 def/Pch-y 0 def/Text-y 0 def
X    /LineTypes [ % in default units
X        [] [1 2] [4 4] [8 4] [13 3] [16 2 2 2] [8 2 2 2] [1 13] [6 5] [12 4]
X    ] def
X    /Attr 5 dict def/CurSc 1 def/Penup false def/XEQ{}def
}bd
/Rem{2 copy div floor mul sub floor cvi}bd
/RastersPerPoint{RastersPerInch 72 div}bd
/ScaleArray{/Factor exch def /Array exch def
X    0 1 Array length 1 sub
X    {dup Array exch get Factor mul Array 3 1 roll put}for}bd
/Coord{Region aload pop /uy exch def /ux exch def /ly exch def /lx exch def
X    uy ly sub ux lx sub Landscape{exch}if /Width exch def /Height exch def
X    lx ly translate Landscape{90 rotate 0 Height neg translate}if
X    1 RastersPerPoint div dup scale}bd
/SetPchSize{gsave
X    newpath 0 0 moveto Pch false charpath flattenpath pathbbox
X    exch 3 1 roll
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-y exch def
X    add 2 div neg /Pch-x exch def
X    grestore}bd
/Show{Outline{false charpath E}{{show}BWOp}ifelse}bd
/SimpleShow{0 Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto Show}bd
/FancyShow{
X    /RotDiff exch def
X    /Cos RotDiff cos abs def
X    /Sin RotDiff sin abs def
X    {
X        ( ) dup 0 4 -1 roll put
X        dup stringwidth pop /CharWidth exch def
X        Cos 0 eq{
X            Text-y Sin div
X        }{
X            Sin 0 eq{
X                CharWidth Cos div
X            }{
X                Text-y Sin div dup
X                CharWidth Cos div dup
X                4 1 roll lt{exch pop}{pop}ifelse
X            }ifelse
X        }ifelse 2 div /CharDist exch def
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X        gsave
X            RotDiff rotate
X            CharWidth 2 div neg Text-y 2 div neg rmoveto
X            Show
X        grestore
X        CharDist 0 translate 0 0 moveto
X    }forall
}bd
/TextShow{
X    CharRot StringRot sub dup 0 eq{pop SimpleShow}{FancyShow}ifelse
}bd
/BoxClip{/CLW currentlinewidth def
X    2{CLW add 4 1 roll}repeat
X    2{CLW sub 4 1 roll}repeat
X    % initclip
X    saveAt grestore gsave restAt
X    newpath 2 index exch 2 index exch dup 6 index exch
X    moveto 3{lineto}repeat closepath clip newpath}bd
/Subregion{
X    7 dict begin/A exch def/Uy exch def/Ux exch def/Ly exch def/Lx exch def
X    Ux Lx sub A 0 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 1 get mul Ly add
X    Ux Lx sub A 2 get mul Lx add
X    Uy Ly sub A 3 get mul Ly add end}bd
/SetFigure{Page aload pop Figure Subregion}bd
/SetPlot{SetFigure Plot Subregion}bd
/SetClip{ClipToPlot{SetPlot}{SetFigure}ifelse BoxClip}bd
/SetPage{0 0 Width Height Page astore RastersPerPoint ScaleArray}bd
/PageBegin{save /PageContext exch def /InPage true def gsave}bd
/PageEnd{grestore PageContext restore /InPage false def}bd
/SImage{
X    dup /Bits exch def 8 exch idiv /PerByte exch def
X    /Ht exch def /Wid exch def
X    1 Wid div 1 Ht div scale
X    /saveSc CurSc def /Colors IColors def
X    /curstr Wid PerByte add 1 sub PerByte idiv string def
X    /MaskByte 16#ff Bits 8 sub bitshift def
X    1 1 Ht{
X        currentfile curstr readhexstring pop pop
X        /CurPos 0 def
X        /Left PerByte def
X        1 1 Wid{
X            Left PerByte eq{
X                /CurByte curstr CurPos get def
X                /MaskMove -8 Bits add def
X                /CurPos CurPos 1 add def
X            }if
X            CurByte MaskMove bitshift MaskByte and
X            dup 0 gt{
X                Sc
X                exch dup 3 1 roll B M 1 z 1 w 1 y F
X            }{pop pop}ifelse
X            Left 1 sub dup /Left exch def 0 le
X            {/Left PerByte def}
X            {/MaskMove MaskMove Bits add def}ifelse
X        }for
X        pop
X    }for
X    /Colors GColors def saveSc Sc
}bd
/Ic {} bd
/Sc {
X    dup dup 1 lt exch 0 ge and
X    {1 exch sub setgray}  % explicit gray level [0,1)
X    {1 sub Colors dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     dup type /arraytype eq {aload pop setrgbcolor} {setgray} ifelse
X    } ifelse
} bd
/If {} bd
/Sf {dup 0 lt /Outline exch def abs
X     1 sub Fonts dup 3 1 roll length Rem floor get
X     findfont PointSize Cex mul RastersPerPoint mul scalefont dup setfont
X     dup /FontMatrix get /Matrix exch def /FontBBox get aload pop
X     Matrix transform 4 2 roll Matrix transform
X     exch pop add /Text-y exch def pop SetPchSize} bd
% fixed controlling parameters
/Landscape true def
/Region [20.88 35.0886 591.12 756.911] def
/bw statusdict begin /processcolors where
{pop processcolors} {1} ifelse end 1 eq
X def
/RastersPerInch 300 def
/PointSize 14 def
/Fonts [
X	/Helvetica
X	/Courier
X	/Times-Roman
X	/Helvetica-Oblique
X	/Helvetica-Bold
X	/Helvetica-BoldOblique
X	/Courier-Oblique
X	/Courier-Bold
X	/Courier-BoldOblique
X	/Times-Italic
X	/Times-Bold
X	/Times-BoldItalic
X	/Symbol
X	/AvantGarde-Book
X	/AvantGarde-BookOblique
X	/AvantGarde-Demi
X	/AvantGarde-DemiOblique
X	/Bookman-Demi
X	/Bookman-DemiItalic
X	/Bookman-Light
X	/Bookman-LightItalic
X	/Helvetica-Narrow
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Bold
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-BoldOblique
X	/Helvetica-Narrow-Oblique

X	/NewCenturySchlbk-BoldItalic

X 1390 54 a @beginspecial 20 @llx
